{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>In this game, unleash your creativity</u></strong> in a world where each element can generate new ones. Play, combine, and discover a vast array of combinations, each holding the potential for unexpected transformations. Your inventiveness is the key to evolving this universe, unlocking achievements, and seeing your discoveries come to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262420/extras/Movie_1920x1080_2024-10-25_007.gif?t=1737052911\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you dive into this sandbox environment, <u><strong>explore the interactions between elements and have fun experimenting with new ideas</strong></u>. No path is predetermined: the adventure is entirely in your hands, and each session offers a chance to reveal new possibilities and mysteries. Each achievement unlocks extra insights, enriching your experience and bringing you closer to mastering this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262420/extras/Movie_1920x1080_2024-10-25_019.gif?t=1737052911\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>But be careful: every combination has its consequences</strong></u>. Some actions might trigger unexpected events that will significantly transform the game. As you manipulate elements, be aware that certain combinations could disrupt the balance of your world. Ready to take on the challenge?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Play with the power of Zeus !","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3262420/094cd3ebe7f14b5cfc402ff83b5fc4749f4c3d33.jpg"},{"name":"Become a gardener !","path":"https://cdn.akam